{"tid":913013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ive 臭閪","createTime":"2018-11-23T05:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T06:51:49.000Z","uid":173073,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4cec13f3068bbde0d7f48abd885b0f7e5e74b096","tid":913013,"uid":173073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:48:27.000Z","msg":"以下件事係個fd同我講<br />\n<br />\n話說呢個臭閪，就係青大(青衣ive )讀，佢呢平時就無咩嘢。但係有一次，佢同我個fd一齊做project,呢條臭閪竟然係做自由人，搞到我個fd 好撚燥，佢好鐘意幫手改啲gramma 啦，但係自己d grammar 都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我個fd 個次比佢改到想屌柒佢，不過費撚事屌鳩佢。除左呢件事之外，呢條臭閪係都不斷收兵，sem1就已經收左一件。佢本有條仔，都不斷係到收兵。有不斷係到用啲特別講野方式去氹人，無組就係都嗲人。最撚好笑嘅係佢竟然係hall🐔，我個fd 咪話樣又哀，身材又無。真係笑撚死佢"},{"pid":"ad1517bdd1fabce383f1d8b1b483b3de08edabc3","tid":913013,"uid":151557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"So what?"},{"pid":"29491b6b0fcd127d867c0fd359dd863421d755ca","tid":913013,"uid":27866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"高質post。"},{"pid":"0983decf75024a109d66a3345de6bfe06e735643","tid":913013,"uid":196092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:56:41.000Z","msg":"I&rsquo;ve Chau-Hied <br />\n<br />\n幫你執好左"},{"pid":"aae54434cfd600f04b83a84011acfe64774cd953","tid":913013,"uid":18607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"圖呢？"},{"pid":"385828841ab29caeb2604ad719fe1f87ed512900","tid":913013,"uid":92273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:01:20.000Z","msg":"拖鞋?"},{"pid":"11f8b3f1d184189be64eeae9980700164d73df02","tid":913013,"uid":50789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:01:59.000Z","msg":"學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" c